00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:20,759
Thank you for today.

276
00:17:20,919 --> 00:17:22,239
You're welcome.

277
00:17:23,960 --> 00:17:25,080
I didn't expect you...

278
00:17:25,239 --> 00:17:26,600
to look weak,

279
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:28,440
but is manly during that crucial moment.

280
00:17:28,600 --> 00:17:30,080
A cornered cat will scratch people.

281
00:17:30,320 --> 00:17:32,360
You learnt how to joke?

282
00:17:39,159 --> 00:17:40,399
Well,

283
00:17:40,960 --> 00:17:43,960
did you tell Zhou Shi
about your feelings?

284
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:45,600
Yes, I did.

285
00:17:46,039 --> 00:17:47,720
Then what did she say?

286
00:17:48,039 --> 00:17:50,360
She was happy, and said thank you.

287
00:17:53,519 --> 00:17:54,960
Congratulations then.

288
00:17:55,399 --> 00:17:57,720
Sleep early.

289
00:17:57,919 --> 00:17:59,519
I'm going back to my room.

290
00:18:01,119 --> 00:18:04,279
♪ My fringe isn't listening to me well ♪

291
00:18:04,560 --> 00:18:07,560
♪ It isn't like me ♪

292
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:12,560
♪ It's like you instead ♪

293
00:18:17,360 --> 00:18:18,720
This is too much.

294
00:18:19,039 --> 00:18:21,200
You fell asleep, then what about me?

295
00:18:27,239 --> 00:18:28,480
Just sleep and don't move.

296
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:31,119
♪ The "us" that I yearn of ♪

297
00:18:31,320 --> 00:18:35,480
♪ Was "you" as stated by her ♪

298
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:38,200
♪ The "us" that I yearn of ♪

299
00:18:38,399 --> 00:18:42,600
♪ I was the only serious one ♪

300
00:18:42,759 --> 00:18:45,320
♪ The "us" that I yearn of ♪

301
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:54,800
♪ If you didn't tell me firmly... ♪

302
00:18:59,159 --> 00:19:01,840
♪ to trust you ♪

303
00:19:05,560 --> 00:19:06,480
[Zhang Shuai]

304
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:17,080
Zhang Shuai.

305
00:19:17,320 --> 00:19:18,759
The teacher is looking for me?

306
00:19:19,399 --> 00:19:20,680
I'll head there now.

307
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:21,960
Goodbye.

308
00:19:23,239 --> 00:19:25,399
We slept here last night?

309
00:19:25,600 --> 00:19:27,039
Where else?

310
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,999
You fell asleep when we were talking.

311
00:19:29,159 --> 00:19:30,440
I didn't dare to move.

312
00:19:30,600 --> 00:19:33,519
I lied on the sofa for the whole night.

313
00:19:33,759 --> 00:19:35,560
My back aches.

314
00:19:36,119 --> 00:19:38,560
I haven't slept so comfortably for ages.

315
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:41,080
Your legs are comfortable to lay on.

316
00:19:41,399 --> 00:19:43,560
Why don't you let me lay
on them for two more days?

317
00:19:43,800 --> 00:19:45,080
Impossible.

318
00:19:45,360 --> 00:19:46,960
I'll head to college now.

319
00:19:47,600 --> 00:19:48,759
Wait a minute.

320
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:51,119
I'll change and send you there.

321
00:20:06,519 --> 00:20:08,200
The teacher asked me to come in a hurry.
What is it about?

322
00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:09,560
It may be about your credit hours.

323
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:11,200
You've been interning outside...

324
00:20:11,320 --> 00:20:12,560
and didn't go to class.

325
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:14,879
But, there aren't much classes left.

326
00:20:14,999 --> 00:20:16,279
Moreover, I checked my credit hours.

327
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:17,720
Even if I can't get good grades,

328
00:20:17,840 --> 00:20:19,159
I should be able to
pass all the subjects.

329
00:20:19,320 --> 00:20:20,440
I don't know about that.

330
00:20:20,840 --> 00:20:21,639
We're here.

331
00:20:21,759 --> 00:20:24,360
Let the teacher
tell you himself. Let's go.

332
00:20:27,399 --> 00:20:29,320
Sir, Zhou Shi is here.

333
00:20:31,759 --> 00:20:32,879
Sir.

334
00:20:33,039 --> 00:20:34,080
We haven't met in a while.

335
00:20:34,320 --> 00:20:35,919
Yes.

336
00:20:36,080 --> 00:20:37,639
It has been at least six months.

337
00:20:37,879 --> 00:20:40,639
I heard your teacher said that
you haven't been to classes in a while?

338
00:20:40,759 --> 00:20:41,560
Is that right?

339
00:20:41,560 --> 00:20:43,999
Yes, recently I'm busy working.

340
00:20:44,119 --> 00:20:45,080
So, I didn't come often.

341
00:20:45,239 --> 00:20:47,360
But, I handed up all the assignments.

342
00:20:47,519 --> 00:20:48,639
Zhou Shi,

343
00:20:48,840 --> 00:20:51,360
our college won't stop
students from interning,

344
00:20:51,519 --> 00:20:53,159
But, you can't skip classes.

345
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:55,200
There will be an exam soon,
can you pass it?

346
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:57,919
I think so.

347
00:20:58,080 --> 00:20:59,879
You have to pass it.

348
00:20:59,879 --> 00:21:01,560
If you failed that exam,

349
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:03,360
you may be delayed
from graduating, get it?

350
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:04,720
I'll be delayed from graduating?

351
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:09,879
That serious?

352
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:21,159
You're a top student that passed CET-6.

353
00:21:21,360 --> 00:21:23,960
You can't let me failed CET-4.

354
00:21:24,239 --> 00:21:25,560
Help me.

355
00:21:25,759 --> 00:21:28,440
There isn't much to teach.

356
00:21:28,759 --> 00:21:31,039
Just memorise the vocabulary
and you'll pass.

357
00:21:31,200 --> 00:21:32,840
If you can help me pass CET-4,

358
00:21:32,999 --> 00:21:34,440
I'll buy you snacks.

359
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:37,639
How many words did you memorise
the vocabulary list of CET-4?

360
00:21:39,080 --> 00:21:40,560
Abandon(the first word on the list).

361
00:21:46,279 --> 00:21:48,039
Sister Fei Fei,

362
00:21:48,399 --> 00:21:50,039
you're the only one
that can help me now.

363
00:21:50,200 --> 00:21:51,879
I can help you.

364
00:21:52,080 --> 00:21:53,519
But, how should I do so?

365
00:21:53,840 --> 00:21:56,320
Did you pass CET-4?

366
00:21:56,560 --> 00:21:57,720
Yes, in my second year.

367
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:59,119
How is that possible?

368
00:21:59,279 --> 00:22:01,200
You rely on pinyin
to sing English songs.

369
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:02,759
How did you pass the CET-4?

370
00:22:02,999 --> 00:22:04,440
You talk a lot.

371
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:06,440
I have my own ways.

372
00:22:10,960 --> 00:22:13,480
Top student, help me.

373
00:22:13,639 --> 00:22:14,919
Help me take the exam.

374
00:22:20,399 --> 00:22:21,360
I was wrong.

375
00:22:21,560 --> 00:22:23,879
Help me once.

376
00:22:26,279 --> 00:22:27,800
Go to Li Ming Cheng.

377
00:22:28,159 --> 00:22:29,720
Ask him to help you revise for CET-4.

378
00:22:29,879 --> 00:22:31,200
Maybe your relationship...

379
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,600
can get closer.

380
00:22:32,840 --> 00:22:35,440
Yes, what a good idea.

381
00:22:35,639 --> 00:22:36,759
Good luck.

382
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:41,999
CET-4?

383
00:22:42,320 --> 00:22:43,720
Yes, Brother Ming Cheng.

384
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:45,960
You're the only one that
can help me right now.

385
00:22:46,279 --> 00:22:48,320
Didn't I give you...

386
00:22:48,320 --> 00:22:49,879
a book on CET-4 vocabulary last year?

387
00:22:50,279 --> 00:22:52,159
-What is your progress now?
-A.

388
00:22:52,320 --> 00:22:53,600
What?

389
00:22:53,759 --> 00:22:55,119
I finished memorising that.

390
00:22:56,639 --> 00:22:58,480
I'm almost done with B.

391
00:22:59,759 --> 00:23:02,200
Brother Ming Cheng, stop scolding me.

392
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:03,560
I know I was wrong.

393
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:05,239
It's not that I don't want to help you,

394
00:23:05,399 --> 00:23:07,360
but, the company arranged for me...

395
00:23:07,360 --> 00:23:08,519
to go on a business trip.

396
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:10,159
I'm flying out this afternoon.

397
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:11,879
For how long?

398
00:23:12,080 --> 00:23:14,279
About half a month.

399
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,759
That long?

400
00:23:16,239 --> 00:23:17,999
Can you stay?

401
00:23:18,360 --> 00:23:19,720
This is the company's arrangement.

402
00:23:19,879 --> 00:23:21,680
I can't make a decision.

403
00:23:23,399 --> 00:23:24,919
Don't worry.

404
00:23:25,080 --> 00:23:26,639
Actually, the CET-4...

405
00:23:26,639 --> 00:23:28,399
is about vocabulary.

406
00:23:28,560 --> 00:23:31,279
Now, go back and memorise.

407
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:33,279
Memorise as much vocabulary as you can.

408
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:35,080
By the way,

409
00:23:35,320 --> 00:23:38,879
the date of the CET-4
falls on the day after your birthday.

410
00:23:39,080 --> 00:23:40,960
You have to focus on...

411
00:23:41,119 --> 00:23:42,480
preparing for the exam.

412
00:23:42,759 --> 00:23:45,239
Cancel any birthday plans for now.

413
00:23:45,399 --> 00:23:46,560
After I return, I'll celebrate with you.

414
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:47,840
Get it?

415
00:23:48,759 --> 00:23:50,159
Yes.

416
00:23:52,320 --> 00:23:53,399
Good luck.

417
00:24:11,279 --> 00:24:12,840
You can only rely on memorising
if you want to pass CET-4.

418
00:24:12,999 --> 00:24:15,080
What about the exams for your major?

419
00:24:19,560 --> 00:24:20,519
Don't look at me.

420
00:24:20,680 --> 00:24:22,440
Although I like to go to art galleries,

421
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:25,399
but exams and appreciating art
are two different things.

422
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:31,519
Your books are new.

423
00:24:31,759 --> 00:24:33,320
You didn't read them since
they were given to you, right?

424
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:36,239
You can't blame me for that.

425
00:24:36,519 --> 00:24:37,960
There are too many words.

426
00:24:38,159 --> 00:24:39,600
I feel sleepy when I read them.

427
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:43,239
If I knew, then I would've
gone to class.

428
00:24:43,440 --> 00:24:46,200
Getting a few key points
is better than knowing nothing at all.

429
00:24:46,440 --> 00:24:48,879
There are so many people in your class.

430
00:24:49,080 --> 00:24:51,080
Nobody can help you?

431
00:24:51,919 --> 00:24:53,720
I think they are struggling themselves.

432
00:24:53,879 --> 00:24:55,840
They don't have time for me.

433
00:24:56,440 --> 00:24:58,759
Your class monitor, Zhang Shuai.

434
00:24:58,919 --> 00:25:00,999
He has good results, right?
Ask him to help you.

435
00:25:01,159 --> 00:25:04,560
Yes, why didn't I think of him?

436
00:25:05,320 --> 00:25:07,800
Help you revise for the exam?
No problem.

437
00:25:09,159 --> 00:25:10,159
I know that...

438
00:25:10,279 --> 00:25:12,480
I can rely on you.

439
00:25:12,999 --> 00:25:14,360
Then...

440
00:25:14,519 --> 00:25:16,360
What subject should we start from?

441
00:25:16,519 --> 00:25:17,800
You can make the decision.

442
00:25:17,999 --> 00:25:19,480
I don't know anything.

443
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:21,560
Okay then.

444
00:25:21,560 --> 00:25:23,600
I'll make a study plan.

445
00:25:23,600 --> 00:25:25,840
From tomorrow onwards,
we'll start with the revision.

446
00:25:25,999 --> 00:25:27,680
I think for the next 15 days,

447
00:25:27,800 --> 00:25:29,279
you'll have to stay in the study room.

448
00:25:29,399 --> 00:25:32,399
I'm prepared to sleep in the study room.

449
00:25:33,360 --> 00:25:35,360
Can you take leave from your company?

450
00:25:35,560 --> 00:25:37,919
I remember that your job
is quite important.

451
00:25:39,039 --> 00:25:41,720
If it doesn't work out,
I'll have to resign.

452
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:46,480
You want to take a 15 days leave?

453
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:49,519
Yes, my exams are starting soon.

454
00:25:49,639 --> 00:25:50,960
And the CET-4 too.

455
00:25:51,239 --> 00:25:53,999
So, I have to focus on revising.

456
00:25:55,119 --> 00:25:56,440
Now that you say that,

457
00:25:56,600 --> 00:25:58,800
I almost forgot that
you're still a student.

458
00:25:58,999 --> 00:26:00,440
But, you're my personal assistant.

459
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:03,159
If you leave, what about work?

460
00:26:03,600 --> 00:26:05,039
I know that this will delay work,

461
00:26:05,200 --> 00:26:06,560
but I have no other way.

462
00:26:06,759 --> 00:26:09,119
If I don't pass my exams this time,

463
00:26:09,320 --> 00:26:10,879
I may be held back from graduating.

464
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:13,320
So, if I can't take a leave,

465
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:14,879
I'll have to resign.

466
00:26:16,080 --> 00:26:18,480
What's the difference between
resigning and taking leave?

467
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:19,999
You can't work either way.

468
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:22,960
If you're busy,

469
00:26:23,119 --> 00:26:25,039
why don't you hire Senior Ran Yu again?

470
00:26:27,800 --> 00:26:29,879
You come out with good ideas.

471
00:26:30,600 --> 00:26:32,960
Fine, don't say that I'm cruel.

472
00:26:33,159 --> 00:26:34,999
I'll approve your leave.

473
00:26:35,360 --> 00:26:38,080
But, you'll have to handover
your work to Wei An.

474
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,999
Thank you, chairman.

475
00:26:41,039 --> 00:26:42,720
And,

476
00:26:42,999 --> 00:26:45,080
the treatment may need to be delayed.

477
00:26:45,639 --> 00:26:46,800
I'm sorry.

478
00:26:47,960 --> 00:26:48,999
It's fine.

479
00:26:49,360 --> 00:26:50,680
I waited for 10 years.

480
00:26:50,879 --> 00:26:52,399
Half a month is nothing.

481
00:26:52,560 --> 00:26:53,960
Take your exam in peace.

482
00:26:54,159 --> 00:26:56,080
Yes, thank you Chairman.

483
00:27:04,440 --> 00:27:05,759
This is the study plan.

484
00:27:05,919 --> 00:27:07,480
Memorise all of them.

485
00:27:10,320 --> 00:27:12,919
How can I memorise all of them?

486
00:27:13,080 --> 00:27:14,320
This is only for one subject.

487
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:17,519
I didn't have much time,
so I only prepared these last night.

488
00:27:18,800 --> 00:27:20,759
Oh dear, just kill me.

489
00:27:20,919 --> 00:27:23,239
Why do I have to memorise
so much vocabulary for CET-4?

490
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:25,480
I won't finish memorising them.

491
00:27:25,759 --> 00:27:27,440
It's useless to worry.

492
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:29,519
We can make last minute preparations...

493
00:27:29,720 --> 00:27:30,999
and cram as much as we can.

494
00:27:31,200 --> 00:27:32,999
Enough, let's start.

495
00:27:33,639 --> 00:27:38,279
♪ I might lose the courage
of the sun sometimes ♪

496
00:27:39,759 --> 00:27:44,039
♪ Even if I fall and my wings are wet ♪

497
00:27:45,320 --> 00:27:50,080
♪ I'll never stop dreaming ♪

498
00:27:51,600 --> 00:27:56,960
♪ We'll cry sometimes ♪
♪ Just like the heavy rain ♪

499
00:27:57,519 --> 00:28:02,200
♪ I'll walk with you under the rain ♪

500
00:28:02,360 --> 00:28:05,840
♪ We'll look at the rainbow
when the rain stops ♪

501
00:28:06,039 --> 00:28:08,800
♪ And look while happiness
slowly settles in ♪

502
00:28:08,999 --> 00:28:13,800
♪ Let's hold hands and
turn into wind that soars to the sky ♪

503
00:28:14,080 --> 00:28:17,879
♪ Let's fly into that starry sky... ♪

504
00:28:17,879 --> 00:28:20,999
♪ to light up our dreams ♪

505
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:29,399
♪ You gave me the strength to smile ♪

506
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:43,239
♪ There might be a shower
during clear and cloudy day ♪

507
00:28:44,560 --> 00:28:49,519
♪ We'll see unexpected
fine view sometimes ♪

508
00:28:50,840 --> 00:28:55,759
♪ Dry the wings you wet with tears ♪

509
00:28:56,399 --> 00:29:01,840
♪ Soar with the wind comes ♪

510
00:29:02,759 --> 00:29:08,159
♪ We'll cry sometimes ♪
♪ Just like the heavy rain ♪

511
00:29:08,600 --> 00:29:14,480
♪ I'll walk with you under the rain ♪

512
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:37,759
Wei An.

513
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:42,639
What's wrong?

514
00:29:43,320 --> 00:29:44,840
Is there a problem with the document?

515
00:29:45,639 --> 00:29:46,759
No.

516
00:29:48,399 --> 00:29:49,759
How many days has it been
since Zhou Shi left?

517
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:51,279
About five days?

518
00:29:52,720 --> 00:29:54,200
Just five days?

519
00:29:55,119 --> 00:29:57,440
Why do I feel like she has been
gone for a long time?

520
00:29:58,800 --> 00:30:00,560
Do we have anything scheduled
this afternoon?

521
00:30:00,840 --> 00:30:01,999
No.

522
00:30:02,279 --> 00:30:03,320
Great.

523
00:30:03,879 --> 00:30:05,600
Then, go to the college with me.

524
00:30:15,039 --> 00:30:16,320
A few days have passed.

525
00:30:16,519 --> 00:30:18,279
But, you only memorised
the contents of two lectures.

526
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:19,560
If this continues,

527
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:20,759
you won't be able to finish memorising.

528
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:22,600
I did try my best to memorise.

529
00:30:22,840 --> 00:30:24,759
I stayed up until 2 to 3 a.m.
for the past two days.

530
00:30:24,999 --> 00:30:26,519
I clearly remembered it all then,

531
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:28,759
but I forgot everything
when I woke up in the morning.

532
00:30:30,680 --> 00:30:32,239
It may be my problem.

533
00:30:32,399 --> 00:30:33,999
I can't help you out anymore.

534
00:30:34,879 --> 00:30:36,159
Don't do this.

535
00:30:36,159 --> 00:30:37,879
Sit down.

536
00:30:38,759 --> 00:30:39,919
It's all my fault.

537
00:30:40,039 --> 00:30:41,720
I'll memorise them all now, okay?

538
00:30:45,999 --> 00:30:46,999
Let's go.

539
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:49,639
We'll go and visit Professor Yan.

540
00:30:52,960 --> 00:30:55,519
What? You won't help me revise anymore?

541
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:56,320
Yes.

542
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:59,399
Professor Yan needs me for a
temporary observation project.

543
00:30:59,759 --> 00:31:01,680
I couldn't reject him.

544
00:31:02,159 --> 00:31:04,080
Then, what about me?

545
00:31:06,200 --> 00:31:08,159
Why don't you ask Teacher Xiao?

546
00:31:08,360 --> 00:31:09,919
Actually, delaying graduation
for one year is nothing serious.

547
00:31:10,119 --> 00:31:11,200
You'll have one year to revise.

548
00:31:11,320 --> 00:31:12,519
That way, you're more
likely to pass the exams.

549
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:15,200
Moreover, you have a job now.

550
00:31:15,399 --> 00:31:16,680
Even if you don't have
your graduation certificate for now,

551
00:31:16,800 --> 00:31:18,200
it won't affect you.

552
00:31:19,080 --> 00:31:20,440
But...

553
00:31:20,560 --> 00:31:21,919
It's my bad.

554
00:31:22,039 --> 00:31:22,919
Well,

555
00:31:23,080 --> 00:31:24,800
you can have the notes.

556
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:26,039
Memorise as much as you can.

557
00:31:26,360 --> 00:31:28,080
I can only help you this much.

558
00:31:28,239 --> 00:31:29,399
I'm sorry.

559
00:31:32,119 --> 00:31:34,239
No one wants to help me?

560
00:31:34,879 --> 00:31:37,560
What should I do?

561
00:31:38,399 --> 00:31:39,680
Miss Zhou.

562
00:31:42,720 --> 00:31:46,039
Assistant An, why are you here?

563
00:31:46,320 --> 00:31:47,999
I have something to do here.

564
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:51,440
What's wrong?
Did you run into a problem?

565
00:31:51,680 --> 00:31:55,399
What else? Exams.

566
00:31:55,960 --> 00:31:57,360
I think I'll be delayed from graduating.

567
00:31:57,560 --> 00:31:58,639
Delayed from graduating?

568
00:31:59,239 --> 00:32:00,080
Why?

569
00:32:00,239 --> 00:32:03,360
Didn't you find someone
to help you revise?

570
00:32:03,600 --> 00:32:06,560
They are busy and
don't have time for me.

571
00:32:09,680 --> 00:32:10,999
I know someone...

572
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:12,840
who majored in arts...

573
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:14,039
when he was studying in the States.

574
00:32:14,239 --> 00:32:16,279
His English is good too.

575
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:17,960
Maybe he can be of help.

576
00:32:18,080 --> 00:32:19,999
Of course, who is he?

577
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:47,200
Come in.

578
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:56,080
Hello, Chairman.

579
00:32:56,239 --> 00:32:58,800
You've been hanging outside
the door for a long time.

580
00:32:59,159 --> 00:33:01,399
Is it that hard to ask for my help?

581
00:33:01,600 --> 00:33:03,039
Assistant An told you all about it?

582
00:33:03,200 --> 00:33:04,119
Yes, he did.

583
00:33:04,239 --> 00:33:06,239
But, I want to hear it from you.

584
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:10,200
Well, Chairman,

585
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:11,680
can you please...

586
00:33:11,800 --> 00:33:13,239
help me revise for my major?

587
00:33:13,360 --> 00:33:15,800
-Sure.
-Really? You agree to it?

588
00:33:16,039 --> 00:33:17,440
Do you want me to reject you?

589
00:33:17,639 --> 00:33:18,840
No, I didn't expect you to...

590
00:33:18,840 --> 00:33:20,279
agree that fast.

591
00:33:21,200 --> 00:33:22,800
Of course there is a condition.

592
00:33:23,840 --> 00:33:24,960
From now onwards,

593
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:26,159
you have to obey my orders...

594
00:33:26,159 --> 00:33:28,320
24/7 no matter what.

595
00:33:28,519 --> 00:33:30,239
If you disagree or fail to do it,

596
00:33:30,399 --> 00:33:32,999
the revision will
stop immediately, okay?

597
00:33:34,119 --> 00:33:35,639
Fine, if you disagree, forget it then.
You can leave now.

598
00:33:35,639 --> 00:33:37,840
No, I can do it...

599
00:33:38,600 --> 00:33:40,999
Okay, we'll start tonight.

600
00:33:41,159 --> 00:33:42,320
Come to my house tonight.

601
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:45,919
I'll let you experience
training from hell.

602
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:47,159
Hell?

603
00:33:47,320 --> 00:33:50,279
By the way, I'll help you
with the CET-4 too.

604
00:33:56,039 --> 00:33:57,320
What is this?

605
00:33:57,519 --> 00:33:58,480
A test...

606
00:33:58,639 --> 00:34:00,239
to test your level now.

607
00:34:00,360 --> 00:34:01,919
Where did you get the questions from?

608
00:34:01,919 --> 00:34:03,720
I set the questions myself. Okay.

609
00:34:03,840 --> 00:34:05,480
I'll give you 20 minutes...

610
00:34:05,600 --> 00:34:06,680
to finish this.

611
00:34:07,639 --> 00:34:09,199
You can start now.

612
00:34:22,679 --> 00:34:23,840
Five minutes have passed.

613
00:34:39,120 --> 00:34:40,320
Eight minutes.

614
00:34:43,679 --> 00:34:44,840
10 minutes.

615
00:34:57,719 --> 00:34:59,199
Five more minutes left.

616
00:35:04,920 --> 00:35:09,120
Five, four, three, two,

617
00:35:09,759 --> 00:35:11,199
-one.
-Wait.

618
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:13,040
[CET-4]

619
00:35:13,120 --> 00:35:16,360
-Your handwriting is terrible.
-It won't affect my marks.

620
00:35:16,640 --> 00:35:18,439
If your handwriting can't be read,
marks will be deducted.

621
00:35:39,199 --> 00:35:41,160
There's only half a month left, right?

622
00:35:45,679 --> 00:35:47,400
If it won't work, forget it.

623
00:35:47,679 --> 00:35:49,239
I'll just delay from graduating.

624
00:35:51,679 --> 00:35:53,759
It's not for you to decide now.

625
00:35:53,959 --> 00:35:56,199
From today onwards, stay here.

626
00:35:57,199 --> 00:35:58,080
I don't think you have...

627
00:35:58,080 --> 00:35:59,719
much time to sleep.

628
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:04,800
Do you have to
do this just for revising?

629
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:08,519
Do you have to stay at his house?
It'll be more convenient for revision.

630
00:36:08,880 --> 00:36:10,360
He lives upstairs
and you live downstairs.

631
00:36:10,360 --> 00:36:12,039
How inconvenient can that be?

632
00:36:12,959 --> 00:36:15,279
Is he trying to use this opportunity
to get closer to you?

633
00:36:16,759 --> 00:36:18,279
Maybe.

634
00:36:18,519 --> 00:36:20,160
Why are you so calm?

635
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:23,039
Since he moved here,
I thought that was abnormal.

636
00:36:23,199 --> 00:36:24,560
He has a huge mansion
but wouldn't stay there.

637
00:36:24,679 --> 00:36:26,199
He insisted on living in this old house.

638
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:29,759
-Is he still thinking of pursuing you?
-Don't worry.

639
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:31,600
He wouldn't think of that.

640
00:36:33,080 --> 00:36:34,759
That was all a misunderstanding.

641
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:35,999
Now, it's all resolved.

642
00:36:36,160 --> 00:36:37,999
We're just friends.

643
00:36:38,759 --> 00:36:40,360
Don't let your guard down.

644
00:36:40,560 --> 00:36:43,519
This is a classical technique
used by men...

645
00:36:43,679 --> 00:36:45,199
