652
00:36:55,959 --> 00:36:57,400
He told you everything?

653
00:36:57,560 --> 00:36:59,120
He told me to keep it a secret.

654
00:36:59,560 --> 00:37:00,519
As if.

655
00:37:00,719 --> 00:37:02,719
Who do you think planned the meeting?

656
00:37:02,880 --> 00:37:04,840
If I didn't plan it well,

657
00:37:05,039 --> 00:37:06,600
