658
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:08,679
Really? Thank you.

659
00:37:08,840 --> 00:37:11,360
Do you know how long did I wait for him?
He refused to say it.

660
00:37:11,560 --> 00:37:13,160
You knew it already?

661
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:15,719
I was waiting for him to say it.

662
00:37:17,360 --> 00:37:20,279
Fine, you knew about it.

663
00:37:20,560 --> 00:37:21,999
I was foolish...

664
00:37:21,999 --> 00:37:23,560
not to discover anything.

665
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:25,640
I even fantasized.

666
00:37:25,880 --> 00:37:28,800
It's different, since you
didn't really notice him.

667
00:37:28,959 --> 00:37:30,199
Fine.

668
00:37:30,439 --> 00:37:31,880
I can't be compared to you.

669
00:37:32,880 --> 00:37:34,160
This is good.

670
00:37:34,479 --> 00:37:36,719
I thought you'll only like
Li Ming Cheng in this lifetime.

671
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:38,479
How can they be the same?

672
00:37:38,679 --> 00:37:40,080
Xiao Fei...

673
00:37:40,880 --> 00:37:44,560
has always been my idol.

674
00:37:48,479 --> 00:37:50,600
No matter what, all the best to you.

675
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:54,439
Thank you.

676
00:37:57,840 --> 00:38:00,279
Well, be careful of Wei Qing.

677
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:02,999
Don't worry,
I'm just going to revise there.

678
00:38:03,160 --> 00:38:04,600
I'll be back after half a month.

679
00:38:04,759 --> 00:38:06,880
If you miss me, come up anytime.

680
00:38:15,239 --> 00:38:16,439
Where are you going?

681
00:38:17,439 --> 00:38:18,959
Your Sister Zhou Shi
is moving upstairs...

682
00:38:18,959 --> 00:38:20,759
to live with Wei Qing.

683
00:38:20,959 --> 00:38:22,039
Are you not going to stop her?

684
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:23,800
Live together?

685
00:38:23,999 --> 00:38:25,519
Don't listen to her talking nonsense.

686
00:38:25,719 --> 00:38:27,279
Your senior is helping me with revision.

687
00:38:27,439 --> 00:38:29,120
So, I'm staying with him.

688
00:38:30,519 --> 00:38:32,360
But, I'll be back after half a month.

689
00:38:32,560 --> 00:38:33,840
So,

690
00:38:33,999 --> 00:38:35,640
you'll have to depend
on Sister Fei Fei to feed you.

691
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:36,959
Take care.

692
00:38:37,160 --> 00:38:39,360
It's fine, I'll order delivery food.

693
00:38:39,560 --> 00:38:41,479
-Good boy.
-What do you mean?

694
00:38:41,479 --> 00:38:42,959
How much do you dislike my cooking?

695
00:38:43,120 --> 00:38:44,840
I improved a lot, okay?

696
00:38:45,080 --> 00:38:47,080
Okay, I'll leave now.

697
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:48,920
Help me say goodbye to the top student.

698
00:38:49,120 --> 00:38:50,439
Don't miss me too much.

699
00:38:50,600 --> 00:38:52,320
Leave, no one will miss you. Go!

700
00:39:01,519 --> 00:39:03,560
Well, you have a big heart.

701
00:39:03,759 --> 00:39:04,920
Your Sister Zhou Shi
has moved upstairs...

702
00:39:04,920 --> 00:39:05,999
to live with another man,

703
00:39:06,120 --> 00:39:07,679
but you're still in the mood
to read a sketchbook?

704
00:39:07,840 --> 00:39:09,160
What's wrong with that?

705
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:12,360
Do you trust Wei Qing or Zhou Shi?

706
00:39:12,560 --> 00:39:14,039
I trust the both of them.

707
00:39:14,679 --> 00:39:16,320
Fine, you're all innocent.

708
00:39:16,479 --> 00:39:18,360
You all have big hearts, okay?

709
00:39:18,519 --> 00:39:20,439
I am the one who think too much.

710
00:39:21,039 --> 00:39:22,759
By the way, do you want supper?

711
00:39:22,920 --> 00:39:24,160
You'll cook?

712
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:26,840
